<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .intro {
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 800px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .intro h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        .intro p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #555;
        }

        .admin-actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 20px auto;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .admin-actions a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .admin-actions a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .ynwa{
            color: #c8102e;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer{
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>Admin Dashboard</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="intro">
        <h2>Welcome, Admin!</h2>
        <p>
            This is your administrator area for the <strong>Liverpool Fan Shop</strong>.
            As an admin, you have the ability to manage products, orders, and users efficiently.
            Whether it's adding new merchandise, reviewing order details, or managing customer data, this dashboard provides you with the tools you need to maintain a smooth-running store.
        </p>
        <p>
            Use the buttons below to navigate to key sections of the shop administration:
            <br><strong>View and manage orders, browse registered users, or update the product catalog.</strong>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="admin-actions">
        <a href="/Admin/Orders/AllOrders">View All Orders</a>
        <a href="/Admin/User/All">View All Users</a>
    </div>

    <div class="ynwa">
        <p>YNWA!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
